OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FReporting by Sam Holder and Olly Denton
OL,8,FA photograph showing Andrew
OL,9,FMountbatten-Windsor and Lord Peter
OL,10,FMandelson wearing bathrobes, alongside
OL,11,Fconvicted paedophile Jeffrey Epstein,
OL,12,Fhas been uncovered by ITV News.
OL,14,FIt is the first known photograph of
OL,15,Fthe three men together.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
