OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FIn the photo, released as part of the
OL,7,FEpstein files, the trio are sitting
OL,8,Faround a wooden table on some decking,
OL,9,Fdrinking out of mugs featuring the US
OL,10,Fflag. They are meeting in Martha's
OL,11,FVineyard, Massachusetts, ITV News
OL,12,Funderstands.
OL,14,FNo time or date is given for the
OL,15,Fphotograph, but it is similar to a
OL,16,Fpicture included in the Epstein
OL,17,F"birthday book", released last year,
OL,18,Fwhich appeared to show Mandelson,
OL,19,Fagain in a bathrobe, and Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
