OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FIn that book, the former UK ambassador
OL,7,Fto the US is alleged to have written a
OL,8,Fletter to the paedophile and sex
OL,9,Ftrafficker in which he describes him
OL,10,Fas his "best pal".
OL,12,FThe photograph is understood to have
OL,13,Fbeen taken between 1999-2000, before
OL,14,FEpstein was imprisoned in 2008 for
OL,15,Fsoliciting prostitution from a minor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
