OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FThe relationships between Mandelson
OL,7,Fand Epstein, and Epstein and Andrew,
OL,8,Fbecame clearer following the release
OL,9,Fof more than three million documents
OL,10,Fin the latest batch of the so-called
OL,11,FEpstein files, including over 2,000
OL,12,Fvideos and 180,000 images.
OL,14,FWhile the files were released on
OL,15,FJanuary 30, the sheer quantity of
OL,16,Fdocuments means that new information
OL,17,Fis still being uncovered.
OL,19,FHow has the government responded?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773479142
OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FThe prime minister has yet to respond
OL,7,Fto the photo, but ITV News has spoken
OL,8,Fto several MPs about the picture.
OL,10,FRachael Maskell, Labour MP for York
OL,11,FCentral, told ITV News the photo
OL,12,Fdemonstrates "these powerful men don't
OL,13,Fconduct themselves in a professional,
OL,14,Fnormal way as we would expect anyone
OL,15,Fin such high office to".
OL,17,F"While providing a backdrop to the
OL,18,Ftoxic culture they inhabited, they
OL,19,Fshould be candid as to what else they
OL,20,Fknew of the environment in which many
OL,21,Fwomen were exploited and abused."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
