OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773479142
OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FPaula Barker, Labour MP for Liverpool
OL,7,FWavertree, described the picture as
OL,8,F"absolutely sickening".
OL,10,F"It shows three very depraved
OL,11,Findividuals who think that they're
OL,12,Fabove the law and they're having a
OL,13,Fwhale of a time. I think it's quite
OL,14,Fdisgusting to be perfectly honest."
OL,16,FMandelson and Epstein
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
