OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FOn the eve of Epstein's arrest in
OL,7,F2008, Mandelson sent emails urging him
OL,8,Fto "fight for early release" and
OL,9,Fpromised: "Your friends stay with you
OL,10,Fand love you."
OL,12,FIn 2009, Mandelson stayed at Epstein's
OL,13,FNew York apartment while the convicted
OL,14,Fsex offender served his 18-month
OL,15,Fprison sentence.
OL,17,FEmails later appeared to show
OL,18,FMandelson's husband, Reinaldo Avila da
OL,19,FSilva, thanking Epstein for a payment
OL,20,Fof #10,000 to fund an osteopathy
OL,21,Fcourse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
