CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773479142
OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FMessages released from 2009 and 2010
OL,7,Fappeared to show Mandelson, the then
OL,8,Fbusiness secretary in Gordon Brown's
OL,9,Fgovernment, discussing sensitive
OL,10,Fgovernment issues with Epstein,
OL,11,Fincluding advance notice of a E500
OL,12,Fbillion bailout to save the Euro.
OL,14,FFollowing the release of the files,
OL,15,FMandelson was arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fmisconduct in public office on
OL,17,FFebruary 23 and then released on bail.
OL,19,FHe has said, via lawyers, that he
OL,20,Flooks forward to clearing his name.
