OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FIn response to the latest Epstein
OL,7,Fdocuments released, Mandelson gave the
OL,8,Fsame statement he did to BBC Newsnight
OL,9,Fon January 12.
OL,11,FHe said: "I was wrong to believe
OL,12,FEpstein following his conviction and
OL,13,Fto continue my association with him
OL,14,Fafterwards. I apologise unequivocally
OL,15,Ffor doing so to the women and girls
OL,16,Fwho suffered."
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, the UK government
OL,19,Freleased its first set of documents
OL,20,Frelating to Mandelson's appointment as
OL,21,Fambassador to the United States.
