OL,3,CITV News uncovers first known photo of
OL,4,CAndrew, Mandelson and Epstein together
OL,6,FAlso among the correspondence between
OL,7,Fthe pair was an invitation for Epstein
OL,8,Fto dine at Buckingham Palace,
OL,9,FEpstein's offer to introduce Andrew to
OL,10,Fa 26-year-old Russian woman, and
OL,11,Fphotos that appear to show the former
OL,12,Fprince kneeling over an unidentified
OL,13,Fwoman lying on the floor.
OL,15,FAndrew's name appeared at least
OL,16,Fseveral hundred times in the document
OL,17,Frelease.
OL,19,FHe has consistently denied any
OL,20,Fwrongdoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
